# =============================================================================
# .trivyignore - Suppress specific CVEs/findings after risk assessment
# =============================================================================
# Format: CVE-ID atau finding ID, satu per baris
# PENTING: Setiap entry HARUS punya justifikasi dan ticket reference
#
# Template:
# CVE-XXXX-XXXXX  # [TICKET-123] Justifikasi: alasan kenapa di-ignore
# =============================================================================

# --- Accepted Risks ---
# Tambahkan CVE yang sudah di-review dan diterima risikonya di sini.
# Contoh:
# CVE-2023-12345  # [SEC-001] False positive: library tidak digunakan di code path yang vuln
# CVE-2024-67890  # [SEC-002] Mitigated: sudah ada WAF rule yang block exploit ini

# --- Spring Boot DevTools (development only, tidak masuk production) ---
# Jika ada CVE terkait devtools, bisa di-ignore karena scope=runtime,optional

# --- Test Dependencies ---
# CVE pada test-scope dependencies bisa di-assess terpisah
